trans-unit.source: Represents the navigation of a relationship.
The result of this expression is the result of navigating the relationship.
trans-unit.target: 此表达式的结果是关系的导航结果。

trans-unit.source: Implements the visitor pattern for expressions that do not produce a result value.
trans-unit.target: 实现不生成结果值的表达式的访问者模式。

trans-unit.source: Gets the metadata for the relationship end to navigate from.
trans-unit.target: 获取要从导航的关系 end 的元数据。

trans-unit.source: The metadata for the relationship end to navigate from.
trans-unit.target: 要从导航的关系 end 的元数据。

trans-unit.source: Gets the metadata for the relationship end to navigate to.
trans-unit.target: 获取要导航到的关系 end 的元数据。

trans-unit.source: The metadata for the relationship end to navigate to.
trans-unit.target: 要导航到的关系 end 的元数据。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets an <xref href="System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbExpression"></xref> that specifies the starting point of the navigation and must be a reference to an entity instance.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置<xref href="System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbExpression"> </xref> ，它指定导航的起始点并必须是对某个实体实例的引用。

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbExpression"></xref> that specifies the instance of the source relationship end from which navigation should occur.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Data.Common.CommandTrees.DbExpression"> </xref> ，它指定应从中进行导航的源关系 end 的实例。
